rica Music Awards (AFRIMA) 2015 Winners List|url=http://tooxclusive.com/news/all-africa-music-awards-afrima-2015-winners-list/|website=Tooxclusive|publisher=aL Yhusuff|accessdate=9 July 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=AFRIMA Announces Nominees For 2015 \u2022 Channels Television|url=http://www.channelstv.com/2015/08/17/afrima-announces-nominees-for-2015/|website=Channels Television|accessdate=9 July 2016|date=17 August 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[The Headies 2015|The Headies]]\n|Best Vocal Performance (Female) (\"Iwo Nikan\")\n|{{won}}\n|<ref name=\"Full list of winners @ The Headies 2015\" /><ref>{{cite web|last1=Adeleke|first1=Shayo|title=The Headies Awards 2015- Full Nominees List|url=http://www.36ng.com.ng/2015/09/30/the-headies-awards-2015-full-nominees-list/|website=36NG|accessdate=9 July 2016|date=30 September 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[2015 Nigeria Entertainment Awards|Nigeria Entertainment Awards]]\n|Female Artist of the Year\n|{{nom}}\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=Nigeria Entertainment Awards (NEA) Announces 2015 Nominees|url=http://www.naijaloaded.com.ng/2015/06/11/nigeria-entertainment-awards-nea-announces-2015-nominees/|website=Naijaloaded|accessdate=9 July 2016|date=11 June 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Akan|first1=Joey|title=NEA Awards 2015: Check out complete winners List|url=http://pulse.ng/buzz/nea-awards-2015-check-out-complete-winners-list-id4147066.html|accessdate=9 July 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" |2016\n|[[Nigeria Entertainment Awards]]\n|Alternative Artist\n|{{Won}}\n|<ref>{{cite news|title=FULL Nominee List For 2016 Nigerian Entertainment Awards (NEA) {{!}} Nigerian Entertainment Today - Nigeria's Number 1 Entertainment Daily|url=http://thenet.ng/2016/06/full-nominee-list-for-2016-nigerian-entertainment-awards-nea/|accessdate=11 July 2016|date=17 June 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170102011347/http://thenet.ng/2016/06/full-nominee-list-for-2016-nigerian-entertainment-awards-nea/|archive-date=2 January 2017|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n